{"tid":105051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]酒精中毒有幻覺 自劈3刀不治","createTime":"2017-02-02T14:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T04:22:15.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6dda13dc07d6ef076f345f08cd818c423447001c","tid":105051,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170202/56251011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170202%2F56251011&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fc81e34d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170202%2F56251011&h=415153b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170202/56251011</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇常州市大年初一中午，有一名男子在工廠酒後疑酒精上腦，自砍3刀自殺，被妻子發現後送到醫院搶救，最終不治。據悉，當時男子說着有人追殺他，迫於無奈只能自己捅自己，具體死亡原因警方還在調查。<br />\n<br />\n自殺男子姓潘，安微人，今年35歲。據她妻子劉X表示，潘是酒精中毒才會做出這樣過激行為，認識他的工廠同事都知道，他只要一喝酒就會胡說八道、情緒激動。妻子說結婚前他就喜歡喝酒，甚至有時候光喝酒不吃飯，曾在安徽給他看過多次病，都沒看好，還在醫院裡住了一個多月戒酒，平時他只敢在工廠裡貪酒喝，下班時候從小賣部買了酒路上喝完回去，因為回去喝會被妻子制止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feebcdd4b5f7ee23dfff7d98450a7556d82a391e","tid":105051,"uid":20842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"飲左甲醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}